<https://w3id.org/pink/models> rdf:type owl:Ontology ;
                                owl:versionIRI <https://w3id.org/pink/0.0.1/models> ;
                                <http://purl.org/dc/terms/abstract> "The Models module of PINK Annotation Schema providing a taxonomy for models."@en ;
                                <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "The Models module of PINK Annotation Schema"@en ;
                                <https://w3id.org/widoco/vocab#introduction> """
This module is a part of the [PINK Annotation Schema](https://pink-project.github.io/PINK-annotation-schema/widoco/index-en.html).
A model is a useful simplified description of a selected part of the world.

A figure showing how the PINK Annotation Schema categorise models can be found [here](https://pink-project.github.io/PINK-annotation-schema/docs/models.html).
"""@en .

